decks.notes: This deck aims to ramp up mana quickly with the UrzaTron lands and use powerful Planeswalkers like Karn Liberated and Ugin, the Spirit Dragon to control the game. It also includes powerful creatures like Ulamog, the Ceaseless Hunger and Thragtusk for added threats. The deck also includes ways to search for specific lands or artifacts to ensure consistency and can use cards like Noxious Revival and Pulse of Murasa for recursion. Overall, the key concept of this deck is to dominate the game through strong control elements and powerful threats.
